name: Fertilizer
description: A fertilizer is any material of natural or synthetic origin that is applied to soil or to plant tissues to supply plant nutrients.

name: Agricultural Machinery
description: Agricultural machinery refers to the various tools, equipment, and machines used in farming and agriculture to increase efficiency and productivity.

name: Seeds
description: Seed is an undeveloped plant embryo and food reserve enclosed in a protective outer covering. More generally, the term "seed" means anything that can be sown, which may include seed and husk or tuber.
